      "id": "PopularPost31534",
      "post_content": "This compared to [Opposition](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Opposition) kind of shows that blue is still superior in control than white and green combined.  \nOn the other hand, these colors are better in creating creature tokens (even white with [Martial Coup](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Martial Coup) or [Conqueror's Pledge](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Conqueror's Pledge)), and on top of that Ravnica's Selesnia guild is focused on that, making it more useful in block-constructed. ",
      "posted_by": "Mode",
